        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4757",
        "content": "The count paused and meditated.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4757_1811_000063_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4757/1811/4757_1811_000063_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4757",
        "content": "This proposal was all very plausible and nice on the surface, but Sir Norman with his usual penetration and acuteness, looked farther than the surface, and found a flaw.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4757_1811_000066_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4757/1811/4757_1811_000066_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4757",
        "content": "\"Until then, we will have to be, I suppose,\" replied Sir Norman, rather ungraciously taking the hand as if it were red hot, and dropping it again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4757_1811_000068_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4757/1811/4757_1811_000068_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4757",
        "content": "\"Where to?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4757_1811_000069_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4757/1811/4757_1811_000069_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4757",
        "content": "\"To the ruin, where you have already been twice to night.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4757_1811_000072_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4757/1811/4757_1811_000072_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4757",
        "content": "\"Never mind; I have heard it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4757_1811_000073_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4757/1811/4757_1811_000073_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4757",
        "content": "Again Sir Norman paused and meditated.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
